  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tbsp oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Saut\u00e9 onions and bell peppers for 5 minutes until soft.",
    "Add garlic, ginger, turmeric, and red chili flakes; cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in tamarind paste, coconut milk, and salt. Simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add blanched basil leaves and cook for 2 minutes to retain crunch.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning. Serve hot."
